    "verifyText": {
      "id": "lf_help_0",
      "value": "Long-term care insurance provides care in the event that you or a loved one need long-term assistance in a nursing home, at an adult day care facility or at your home. It is designed to cover the cost of assistance with activities of daily living such as dressing, eating, bathing, toileting, getting in and out of bed, etc. This coverage provides peace of mind since long-term care is not covered by traditional health insurance and can become a huge financial burden if you don?t plan ahead. As a starting point, this tool helps you determine the amount of long-term care insurance needed for your specific situation. For further information, please consult an insurance professional."
